    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/ann_druyan_362167",
        "quote": "This planet seems to be in such sorry shape. And I can't ever think about the rest of the universe without coming back home and thinking what the implications for life here would be if we were to really have some definitive proof of extraterrestrial life.",
